'''Danith Jalay''' was [[Captain/Legends|captain]] of the ''[[Elegant Interlude]]'' and an experienced [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] who had a home on [[Nar Shaddaa/Legends|Nar Shaddaa]]. Jalay fought in the [[Battle of Nar Shaddaa (4 BBY)|Battle of Nar Shaddaa]].

